    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small silver coins of Germany and German-speaking territories issued from at least the 13th century until the 19th century in Germany and then as a copper coin in Austria into the 20th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
